1
00:01:37,940 --> 00:01:41,020
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,060 --> 00:01:43,979
[Episode 4]

3
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,070
Sign this before you leave.

4
00:01:47,070 --> 00:01:47,950
You're really going to do this?

5
00:01:47,950 --> 00:01:48,970
I've already signed it.

6
00:01:48,970 --> 00:01:50,900
All that's left is your signature.

7
00:01:56,030 --> 00:01:57,570
I'll sign it when I get to the office.

8
00:01:57,570 --> 00:01:59,710
I'll give it back to you tonight.

9
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:08,400
Lu Zhenzhen, why are you hiding?

10
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:09,820
I'm not hiding.

11
00:02:10,169 --> 00:02:12,000
I'm leaving out of respect for you.

12
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:13,240
Out of respect for me?

13
00:02:13,430 --> 00:02:14,830
That sounds like

14
00:02:14,910 --> 00:02:16,590
I'm the mistress.

15
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:17,960
You've had too much. Let's go back.

16
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:18,800
I haven't even had a drink yet.

17
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,600
How am I drunk?

18
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:20,750
Let go of me.

19
00:02:20,770 --> 00:02:21,820
Let go of me!

20
00:02:21,870 --> 00:02:23,130
What's wrong with you?

21
00:02:23,440 --> 00:02:25,700
You're scared, aren't you, Nie Yucheng?

22
00:02:26,550 --> 00:02:28,790
That's you in the video, right?

23
00:02:29,020 --> 00:02:30,900
It's not some AI face swap, right?

24
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:33,960
It's me.

25
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:36,130
At a critical time like this,

26
00:02:36,150 --> 00:02:37,920
you're still making trouble for yourself?

27
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:39,790
Have you lost your mind?

28
00:02:40,329 --> 00:02:41,520
I don't know why she suddenly...

29
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:43,150
Your promotion to Vice President

30
00:02:43,150 --> 00:02:45,000
was supposed to be announced this week.

31
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,420
Now it's suddenly on hold,

32
00:02:46,420 --> 00:02:48,280
and the group is calling about it.

33
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:54,280
You usually seem quite smart.

34
00:02:54,280 --> 00:02:55,280
How could you, at such a critical moment,

35
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:57,150
do such a stupid thing?

36
00:02:57,210 --> 00:02:59,590
You're just giving them ammo, aren't you?

37
00:03:00,160 --> 00:03:01,030
I don't know why

38
00:03:01,030 --> 00:03:02,520
things turned out like this.

39
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:03,650
I'm sorry. I was wrong.

40
00:03:03,650 --> 00:03:06,250
Go back right now and sort this out.

41
00:03:06,560 --> 00:03:09,860
Deal with your personal scandals.

42
00:03:09,980 --> 00:03:10,910
Stop messing around.

43
00:03:10,910 --> 00:03:12,000
At the corporate group,

44
00:03:12,000 --> 00:03:14,680
I've said all the good things
I could for you.

45
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:17,070
But now that this matter has spread,

46
00:03:17,150 --> 00:03:19,430
your promotion will definitely be delayed.

47
00:03:19,430 --> 00:03:22,340
Whether you get it in the end
depends on your luck.

48
00:03:23,360 --> 00:03:24,910
I'll deal with it immediately.

49
00:03:24,910 --> 00:03:25,910
Thank you, Mr. Hu.

50
00:03:42,870 --> 00:03:43,079
[Divorce Agreement]

51
00:03:43,500 --> 00:03:45,250
[Husband's fingerprint]
[Wife's fingerprint] [Xu Miyu]

52
00:03:49,340 --> 00:03:50,600
Why didn't you sign it?

53
00:03:56,090 --> 00:03:57,370
I'm sorry, Miyu.

54
00:04:00,380 --> 00:04:02,370
I went too far that day.

55
00:04:03,260 --> 00:04:04,810
I didn't really mean it,

56
00:04:05,470 --> 00:04:07,710
but I hurt you in a moment of impulse.

57
00:04:08,670 --> 00:04:10,070
I hope you can forgive me.

58
00:04:15,830 --> 00:04:17,490
I really don't want a divorce.

59
00:04:17,810 --> 00:04:18,690
Miyu,

60
00:04:19,130 --> 00:04:20,160
I love you.

61
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,680
I swear to you,

62
00:04:22,089 --> 00:04:22,930
this time,

63
00:04:23,950 --> 00:04:26,280
I will make a clean break
with Lu Zhenzhen.

64
00:04:26,680 --> 00:04:28,480
I won't do anything to hurt you.

65
00:04:28,860 --> 00:04:29,920
Please believe me.

66
00:04:33,659 --> 00:04:35,130
Do you not want a divorce,

67
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,720
or do you just not want one right now?

68
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,330
What do you mean by that?

69
00:04:41,750 --> 00:04:43,040
I heard

70
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:46,960
your promotion
to vice president got delayed.

71
00:04:47,560 --> 00:04:49,960
Are you waiting until after your promotion

72
00:04:50,220 --> 00:04:51,620
to finalize the divorce?

73
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:02,970
You can't be serious, Xu Miyu.

74
00:05:02,970 --> 00:05:04,700
Do you really hate me that much?

75
00:05:05,400 --> 00:05:07,530
Are you just bent on ruining my career?

76
00:05:08,750 --> 00:05:09,630
Anyway,

77
00:05:09,630 --> 00:05:10,980
