86
00:05:29,780 --> 00:05:31,750
I'm the one who truly has no way out.

87
00:05:32,450 --> 00:05:34,350
If I really take another step back,

88
00:05:34,350 --> 00:05:35,890
then I would really become

89
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:37,450
the parasite you called me.

90
00:05:38,570 --> 00:05:40,210
Living off the job you gave me

91
00:05:40,760 --> 00:05:42,360
without any dignity.

92
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,740
Every day feels like having

93
00:05:43,740 --> 00:05:45,070
