104
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:29,880
We split the savings in half.

105
00:06:30,000 --> 00:06:31,000
Do you agree?

106
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:35,370
The house was bought
by my parents before we got married,

107
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:37,930
so it definitely goes back to them.

108
00:06:38,390 --> 00:06:40,390
The car was bought after we got married,

109
00:06:40,390 --> 00:06:42,000
but you don't know how to drive.

110
00:06:42,000 --> 00:06:43,040
If we sell it,

111
00:06:43,040 --> 00:06:44,300
it won't be worth much.

112
00:06:44,600 --> 00:06:45,830
So the car belongs to me.

113
00:06:45,830 --> 00:06:46,610
Of course,

114
00:06:46,630 --> 00:06:48,560
