117
00:06:53,950 --> 00:06:54,950
You have my salary card.

118
00:06:54,950 --> 00:06:56,000
I'm not talking about your salary.

119
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:56,720
I mean savings.

120
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:58,070
I don't have any savings.

121
00:06:58,070 --> 00:07:00,000
You have my salary card.

122
00:07:01,040 --> 00:07:03,240
You manage all the living expenses.

123
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,510
