124
00:07:04,510 --> 00:07:07,270
The monthly utility bills,
living expenses,

125
00:07:07,750 --> 00:07:09,390
traveling a few times a year,

126
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,600
and various subsidies for your family:

127
00:07:11,600 --> 00:07:14,160
your parents, your sister,
and your brother-in-law.

128
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:17,070
-And travel...
-What about the 150,000 Minghui borrowed?

129
00:07:17,070 --> 00:07:19,270
That should be considered our savings.

130
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:21,120
Half of it should be mine.

131
00:07:22,110 --> 00:07:23,570
You know about that money.

132
00:07:23,600 --> 00:07:24,600
It was given to the hospital,

133
00:07:24,600 --> 00:07:25,870
and it's impossible to get it back.

134
00:07:25,870 --> 00:07:27,470
I don't have any extra money.

135
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:28,660
How about this?

136
00:07:29,430 --> 00:07:31,070
When I have a bit more money,

137
00:07:31,070 --> 00:07:33,240
I will transfer your half of the 75,000

138
00:07:33,510 --> 00:07:35,040
to you in installments.

139
00:07:37,510 --> 00:07:38,040
Nie Yucheng,

140
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,680
