144
00:07:55,330 --> 00:07:56,110
[Investor Information;
Investor Name: Nie Yucheng]

145
00:07:56,130 --> 00:07:57,240
[Project information; Project name:
Blue-chip Stock Investment]

146
00:07:57,260 --> 00:07:58,880
[Source of Funds]
[Breakdown of Fund Usage]

147
00:07:58,940 --> 00:08:00,800
This money is for my investments.

148
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:02,230
I originally thought that if

149
00:08:02,230 --> 00:08:03,750
