153
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:09,500
I'm telling the truth.

154
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:11,040
I didn't mean to hide it from you.

155
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:13,520
I was thinking that when
this investment matures

156
00:08:13,520 --> 00:08:14,600
