157
00:08:15,840 --> 00:08:16,770
I'd give you a surprise.

158
00:08:16,770 --> 00:08:17,620
Okay.

159
00:08:18,280 --> 00:08:19,740
Then according to the terms,

160
00:08:19,740 --> 00:08:21,060
