168
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,000
or did you love my money?

169
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:47,080
I should be the one asking that question.

170
00:08:47,080 --> 00:08:48,270
For all these years,

171
00:08:49,510 --> 00:08:50,960
did you love me,

172
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:53,060
or did you love my selfless devotion?

173
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,380
Wait, what do you mean?

174
00:08:54,380 --> 00:08:55,980
I mean that these 4 million

175
00:08:56,510 --> 00:08:57,610
