182
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,630
Do you hate me that much?

183
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:13,390
Always talking about yourself...

184
00:09:13,390 --> 00:09:14,670
All you ever think about is yourself.

185
00:09:14,670 --> 00:09:16,670
