00:12:53,470 --> 00:12:55,420
Kenny, hope to see you soon.

279
00:12:55,650 --> 00:12:56,530
Goodbye.

280
00:12:57,590 --> 00:12:59,520
♪ Busy and restless ♪

281
00:12:59,990 --> 00:13:03,530
♪ No turning back, no stopping ♪

282
00:13:04,740 --> 00:13:08,910
♪ Our path—do you see it now ♪

283
00:13:10,830 --> 00:13:13,290
♪ Just lift your head, oh ♪

284
00:13:14,510 --> 00:13:16,480
♪ Don't look back ♪

285
00:13:17,510 --> 00:13:19,240
♪ I've already learned ♪

286
00:13:20,010 --> 00:13:23,910
♪ If it's not mine, I won't force it ♪

287
00:13:24,580 --> 00:13:26,280
♪ No matter how you force it ♪

288
00:13:26,900 --> 00:13:30,900
♪ It'll only turn into a long,
endless wait ♪

289
00:13:31,970 --> 00:13:34,710
♪ Waiting to make peace with myself ♪

290
00:13:35,600 --> 00:13:37,860
♪ And waiting to meet someone again ♪

291
00:13:38,760 --> 00:13:40,110
♪ Wave goodbye ♪

292
00:14:14,180 --> 00:14:15,050
Ms. Xu,

293
00:14:15,150 --> 00:14:17,420
Room 1819 is ready for you.

294
00:14:17,480 --> 00:14:18,380
[Purong Hotel]

295
00:14:18,510 --> 00:14:19,910
I don't want 1819.

296
00:14:19,940 --> 00:14:21,200
Please change my room.

297
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:22,710
Okay.

298
00:14:26,900 --> 00:14:27,830
Enjoy your stay.

299
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:28,970
Thank you.

300
00:14:32,840 --> 00:14:34,260
Good evening, ma'am.

301
00:14:35,300 --> 00:14:36,300
This way, please.

302
00:14:43,030 --> 00:14:44,150
Welcome.

303
00:14:48,560 --> 00:14:49,570
Please come in.

304
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:57,960
I'd like to order.

305
00:14:57,960 --> 00:14:59,030
Certainly, ma'am.

306
00:14:59,030 --> 00:15:00,030
To order, please dial...

307
00:15:00,030 --> 00:15:01,290
I want Boston lobster.

308
00:15:03,150 --> 00:15:03,910
Boston lobster.

309
00:15:03,910 --> 00:15:05,870
And bluefin tuna,

310
00:15:05,870 --> 00:15:07,200
stir-fried sea snails,

311
00:15:07,670 --> 00:15:09,200
and wine-marinated crab.

312
00:15:09,220 --> 00:15:10,980
For one person,

313
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:12,030
this might be a bit too much.

314
00:15:12,030 --> 00:15:13,080
It's been exactly 10 years

315
00:15:13,080 --> 00:15:14,150
since I last had a proper seafood meal.

316
00:15:14,150 --> 00:15:16,030
I'm going to eat to
my heart's content today.

317
00:15:16,030 --> 00:15:17,890
And give me a serving of ark shell.

318
00:15:20,250 --> 00:15:21,300
What's going on?

319
00:15:21,750 --> 00:15:22,270
Never mind.

320
00:15:22,270 --> 00:15:24,000
Haven't we seen enough of this?

321
00:15:24,030 --> 00:15:24,670
F&B Department.

322
00:15:24,670 --> 00:15:27,070
A guest on the executive floor
is ordering.

323
00:15:45,300 --> 00:15:47,230
I used to think

324
00:15:47,730 --> 00:15:49,030
that giving all of myself

325
00:15:49,030 --> 00:15:50,600
to another person

326
00:15:50,600 --> 00:15:52,750
was also a form of self-realization.

327
00:15:53,910 --> 00:15:55,480
Until one day I came to my senses

328
00:15:55,480 --> 00:15:56,600
and realized

329
00:15:57,030 --> 00:15:59,860
that I had been
treating myself so carelessly,

330
00:16:00,040 --> 00:16:02,040
losing myself further and further.

331
00:16:02,160 --> 00:16:04,280
Forget about the stomach-soothing meal.

332
00:16:04,280 --> 00:16:06,270
Let your mistress make it for you.

333
00:16:10,000 --> 00:16:12,120
But now I'm going to pick myself up.

334
00:16:12,720 --> 00:16:13,690
Stop ordering her around,

335
00:16:13,690 --> 00:16:14,790
stop criticizing her,

336
00:16:14,790 --> 00:16:16,650
and let her do whatever she wants.

337
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:19,220
I hope she can live

338
00:16:19,870 --> 00:16:22,240
every day for her own happiness.

339
00:16:23,510 --> 00:16:24,600
Xu Miyu,

340
00:16:26,520 --> 00:16:27,610
good job.

341
00:16:28,210 --> 00:16:30,430
♪ That fleeting moment I tried to hold ♪

342
00:16:31,220 --> 00:16:33,890
♪ Let it go when the glass runs dry ♪

343
00:16:35,280 --> 00:16:38,190
♪ Unfinished longings ♪

344
00:16:38,880 --> 00:16:42,010
♪ Drift like fading embers ♪

345
00:16:43,170 --> 00:16:45,290
♪ Still longing for yesterday's glow ♪

346
00:16:46,140 --> 00:16:49,100
♪ Yet sailing into
the ocean's depths at night ♪

347
00:16:50,130 --> 00:16:53,150
♪ Questions without answers ♪

348
00:16:54,080 --> 00:16:56,860
♪ Let them go with the wind ♪

349
00:16:58,050 --> 00:16:59,820
♪ Let them go ♪

350
00:17:53,610 --> 00:17:54,360
Hello?

351
00:17:55,220 --> 00:17:56,600
Clean the room,

352
00:17:57,030 --> 00:17:57,840
now.

353
00:18:02,790 --> 00:18:03,220
Hello,

354
00:18:03,250 --> 00:18:04,530
room service.

355
00:19:56,570 --> 00:19:57,580
[October 31]

356
00:20:06,990 --> 00:20:07,250
[Message]

357
00:20:07,250 --> 00:20:08,850
[Ms. Xu Miyu, we regret to
inform you that your profile

358
00:20:08,870 --> 00:20:10,910
[is not the best fit for this role.]

359
00:20:22,170 --> 00:20:22,590
[Hello, I'm very interested
in the Housekeeping Supervisor position]

360
00:20:22,590 --> 00:20:23,020
[(5-day workweek with 2 days off)...]

361
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:24,460
[JD Cleaning Specialist — 8,000 RMB/month]

362
00:20:24,480 --> 00:20:26,030
[Free training, stable orders]

363
00:20:26,230 --> 00:20:26,790
[JD Hiring Cleaning Specialists Urgently;
8,000 RMB/month]

364
00:20:26,820 --> 00:20:27,480
[Jobs assigned nearby, steady orders]

365
00:20:30,590 --> 00:20:32,020
[Competition Analysis]

366
00:20:34,230 --> 00:20:36,300
[Manting Art Hotel]

367
00:20:36,600 --> 00:20:39,880
[Update on Your Application for
the Assistant General Manager Position]

368
00:20:39,160 --> 00:20:40,240
Hello.

369
00:20:40,240 --> 00:20:41,440
I interviewed

370
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:42,750
at your hotel recently.

371
00:20:42,750 --> 00:20:44,400
My name is Xu Miyu.

372
00:20:44,670 --> 00:20:46,730
I just received the rejection letter.

373
00:20:46,730 --> 00:20:47,960
I would like

374
00:20:48,030 --> 00:20:49,590
to explain a few things.

375
00:20:49,590 --> 00:20:50,880
Could you give me another chance?

376
00:20:50,880 --> 00:20:52,070
I am sorry, ma'am.

377
00:20:52,070 --> 00:20:54,000
The employee we hired
has already started today.

378
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:55,640
Please try other companies.

379
00:20:55,640 --> 00:20:56,240
Goodbye.

380
00:21:04,270 --> 00:21:04,510
Hello.

381
00:21:04,510 --> 00:21:05,640
Mr. Su.

382
00:21:06,750 --> 00:21:07,590
What?

383
00:21:09,230 --> 00:21:10,710
The 8 million is gone?

384
00:21:10,740 --> 00:21:13,870
The opposing lawyer
sent me an investment report today.

385
00:21:14,630 --> 00:21:16,560
This project is currently
suffering severe losses.

386
00:21:16,560 --> 00:21:17,540
Not only is there no profit,

387
00:21:17,540 --> 00:21:19,160
but there is also a debt
of over 2 million.

388
00:21:19,160 --> 00:21:20,440
Mr. Nie stated

389
00:21:20,460 --> 00:21:22,550
that he doesn't plan
to split the debt with you.

390
00:21:22,550 --> 00:21:23,790
He will bear it himself

391
00:21:23,790 --> 00:21:25,590
and wants to negotiate with you.

392
00:21:26,070 --> 00:21:27,890
This is definitely Nie Yucheng's trick.

393
00:21:27,890 --> 00:21:29,660
He just wants to stall and not pay.

394
00:21:29,660 --> 00:21:31,600
But his trick worked.

395
00:21:31,920 --> 00:21:32,790
Why?

396
00:21:32,790 --> 00:21:34,550
Because this amount was in the negative

397
00:21:34,550 --> 00:21:35,960
during your marriage.

398
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:38,030
Even if it turns into a profit later,

399
00:21:38,030 --> 00:21:39,440
according to the Marriage Law,

400
00:21:39,440 --> 00:21:41,310
since your marriage is already dissolved,

401
00:21:41,310 --> 00:21:42,680
it will no longer be considered

402
00:21:42,680 --> 00:21:44,280
your joint property.

403
00:21:44,510 --> 00:21:45,680
Which means

404
00:21:46,400 --> 00:21:47,550
he no longer has to split it with you.

405
00:21:47,550 --> 00:21:48,750
Knowing Nie Yucheng,

406
00:21:48,750 --> 00:21:51,310
he'd never make such a losing investment.

407
00:21:52,310 --> 00:21:54,640
He's obviously transferring his assets.

408
00:21:54,830 --> 00:21:56,440
Can I sue him?

409
00:21:56,440 --> 00:21:57,550
It will take time.

410
00:21:58,200 --> 00:21:59,930
We don't have enough evidence.

411
00:22:00,270 --> 00:22:02,360
Now is not the best time to sue.

412
00:22:02,440 --> 00:22:04,070
I'm not completely sure we can win.

413
00:22:04,070 --> 00:22:05,400
I can find the evidence.

414
00:22:05,730 --> 00:22:07,040
And I can wait.

415
00:22:08,200 --> 00:22:09,550
I must get this money.

416
00:22:10,400 --> 00:22:12,400
Mr. Su, you have to help me.

417
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:19,570
Good morning, ma'am.

418
00:22:19,570 --> 00:22:20,640
Hello. I'd like to check out.

419
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:21,270
Okay.

420
00:22:24,400 --> 00:22:25,440
Did you rest well last night,

421
00:22:25,440 --> 00:22:26,400
Ms. Xu?

422
00:22:27,030 --> 00:22:27,790
It was fine.

423
00:22:28,160 --> 00:22:29,270
Your total comes

424
00:22:29,270 --> 00:22:30,920
to 6,680 yuan.

425
00:22:30,920 --> 00:22:33,030
Would you like to pay by phone or card?

426
00:22:33,030 --> 00:22:34,680
6,680?

427
00:22:35,310 --> 00:22:37,920
Isn't your executive suite only 2,300?

428
00:22:37,920 --> 00:22:38,790
The alcohol in the room

429
00:22:38,790 --> 00:22:41,070
and the meals you ordered
are charged separately.

430
00:22:41,070 --> 00:22:41,830
You ordered

431
00:22:41,830 --> 00:22:43,750
2,190 yuan worth of seafood

432
00:22:43,750 --> 00:22:45,350
and 540 yuan worth of drinks,

433
00:22:45,510 --> 00:22:47,640
plus a 100 yuan room service fee.

434
00:22:48,960 --> 00:22:50,270
Here is your itemized bill.

435
00:22:50,270 --> 00:22:52,750
Then what's the other 1,550 for?

436
00:22:52,750 --> 00:22:54,550
You ruined 2 of our carpets

437
00:22:54,550 --> 00:22:56,200
and a crystal ornament.

438
00:22:56,200 --> 00:22:57,510
So...

439
00:22:57,510 --> 00:22:58,550
I'm sorry.

440
00:22:58,750 --> 00:22:59,680
I forgot.

441
00:22:59,710 --> 00:23:00,640
Ms. Xu.

442
00:23:00,640 --> 00:23:02,790
So, will you pay by phone or card?

443
00:23:02,790 --> 00:23:03,640
WeChat Pay.

444
00:23:10,290 --> 00:23:11,050
Thank you.

445
00:23:15,780 --> 00:23:17,140
Welcome.

446
00:23:18,630 --> 00:23:19,300
I'm sorry.

447
00:23:19,320 --> 00:23:20,040
It's okay.

448
00:23:28,790 --> 00:23:30,280
Thank you for staying with us.

449
00:23:29,400 --> 00:23:32,370
[14 years ago]

450
00:23:32,460 --> 00:23:33,460
[Purong Hotel]

451
00:23:33,550 --> 00:23:34,480
Hello.

452
00:23:34,020 --> 00:23:37,330
[Young Ji Feng]

453
00:23:34,480 --> 00:23:36,070
I'm the new intern starting today.

454
00:23:36,070 --> 00:23:37,550
Where should I report?

455
00:23:37,550 --> 00:23:38,510
Take the staff entrance.

456
00:23:38,510 --> 00:23:39,410
It's right over there.

457
00:23:39,410 --> 00:23:40,440
Okay, thank you.

458
00:23:41,100 --> 00:23:42,030
Welcome aboard,

459
00:23:42,030 --> 00:23:42,890
new colleague.

460
00:23:53,720 --> 00:23:55,250
The elevator is over there.

461
00:23:56,790 --> 00:23:57,960
Hello.

462
00:23:58,630 --> 00:24:00,210
Eighth floor?

463
00:24:04,420 --> 00:24:05,230
Check-in.

464
00:24:06,000 --> 00:24:06,720
Hello, sir.

465
00:24:06,720 --> 00:24:07,510
Welcome.

466
00:24:09,030 --> 00:24:09,960
Mr. Ji.

467
00:24:11,790 --> 00:24:14,310
I see you booked our executive floor.

468
00:24:14,590 --> 00:24:16,480
Would you like to check in early?

469
00:24:16,480 --> 00:24:17,270
Yes.

470
00:24:18,310 --> 00:24:20,840
Then I suggest you
sign up for our membership.

471
00:24:21,460 --> 00:24:21,940
[Join as a VIP for RMB 50,000]

472
00:24:21,960 --> 00:24:22,520
[and enjoy exclusive privileges]

473
00:24:22,750 --> 00:24:25,030
With a membership, you can check in early

474
00:24:25,030 --> 00:24:26,350
and enjoy a 20% discount

475
00:24:26,350 --> 00:24:28,610
at the Western and Chinese restaurants.

476
00:24:28,790 --> 00:24:29,550
No, thanks.

477
00:24:29,750 --> 00:24:31,110
I just want to check in early.

478
00:24:31,110 --> 00:24:32,910
You want me to spend 50,000 yuan?

479
00:24:35,310 --> 00:24:36,310
Check-in for non-members

480
00:24:36,310 --> 00:24:37,960
starts at 2 PM.

481
00:24:38,270 --> 00:24:40,470
I suggest you come back this afternoon.

482
00:24:42,910 --> 00:24:43,210
[Black Card VIP at Purong Hotel]

483
00:24:44,960 --> 00:24:46,090
With this,

484
00:24:46,110 --> 00:24:47,460
can I check in early?

485
00:24:49,040 --> 00:24:50,170
Yes, sir.

486
00:24:50,190 --> 00:24:51,650
I'll handle it for you now.

487
00:25:05,720 --> 00:25:06,890
Hello.

488
00:25:08,590 --> 00:25:09,200
Okay.

489
00:25:09,200 --> 00:25:10,660
I'll send it up right away.

490
00:25:11,270 --> 00:25:11,960
Okay.

491
00:25:16,070 --> 00:25:16,830
It's done.

492
00:25:17,030 --> 00:25:17,720
Thank you.

493
00:25:18,640 --> 00:25:19,480
Thanks.

494
00:25:22,720 --> 00:25:23,610
Cover for me.

495
00:25:23,640 --> 00:25:24,480
Mr. Ji.

496
00:25:25,270 --> 00:25:26,030
Mr. Ji.

497
00:25:26,830 --> 00:25:27,430
Excuse me.

498
00:25:27,880 --> 00:25:28,480
What is it?

499
00:25:28,480 --> 00:25:30,810
You are a Black Card VIP
guest of our hotel.

500
00:25:30,830 --> 00:25:32,070
The system just showed

501
00:25:32,070 --> 00:25:33,550
that you will be staying here
for a long time.

502
00:25:33,550 --> 00:25:34,720
If you don't mind,

503
00:25:34,720 --> 00:25:36,200
I can show you around

504
00:25:36,200 --> 00:25:37,070
to get familiar with the place.

505
00:25:37,070 --> 00:25:38,270
Would you like that?

506
00:25:38,820 --> 00:25:39,580
Sure.

507
00:25:40,140 --> 00:25:41,140
This way, please.

508
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:43,440
Our Purong Hotel

509
00:25:43,440 --> 00:25:45,920
has been established
for nearly half a century.

510
00:25:45,920 --> 00:25:46,720
In Shanghai,

511
00:25:46,720 --> 00:25:49,480
it is a well-known,
established 5-star hotel.

512
00:25:50,880 --> 00:25:51,790
On your right-hand side

513
00:25:51,790 --> 00:25:53,720
is our hotel's banquet hall.

514
00:25:53,790 --> 00:25:55,240
It has hosted

515
00:25:55,240 --> 00:25:56,930
a wide variety of business banquets.

516
00:25:56,930 --> 00:25:58,700
[Young Ji Feng]

517
00:25:57,070 --> 00:25:58,790
It can accommodate

518
00:25:58,790 --> 00:26:00,000
around 200 people.

519
00:26:00,110 --> 00:26:02,030
If you need it in the future,

520
00:26:02,030 --> 00:26:02,790
you can always

521
00:26:02,790 --> 00:26:05,450
contact our front office
to make a reservation.

522
00:26:06,110 --> 00:26:08,000
Over the years, our Purong Hotel

523
00:26:08,000 --> 00:26:09,830
has kept pace with the times.

524
00:26:10,030 --> 00:26:13,110
Both in terms of decor and cuisine,

525
00:26:13,110 --> 00:26:15,510
it combines Chinese and Western elements.

526
00:26:16,110 --> 00:26:17,030
As for the dishes,

527
00:26:17,030 --> 00:26:18,310
we have a variety of flavors.

528
00:26:18,310 --> 00:26:21,270
You can choose
according to your preference.

529
00:26:21,550 --> 00:26:22,750
If you need to,

530
00:26:22,750 --> 00:26:24,790
you can also contact us
for a reservation anytime.

531
00:26:24,790 --> 00:26:26,720
Here is our Western restaurant,

532
00:26:26,720 --> 00:26:28,000
where you can

533
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:30,590
taste delicacies from all over the world.

534
00:26:30,720 --> 00:26:33,110
Our newly introduced
afternoon tea and desserts

535
00:26:33,110 --> 00:26:35,350
are extremely delicious.

536
00:26:35,350 --> 00:26:36,160
If you have time,

537
00:26:36,160 --> 00:26:37,760
you should come and try them.

538
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:46,720
What is that smell?

539
00:26:47,610 --> 00:26:48,610
What?

540
00:26:50,430 --> 00:26:51,390
I feel like

541
00:26:51,440 --> 00:26:52,860
there's a very pungent smell here.

542
00:26:52,860 --> 00:26:53,920
Don't you smell it?

543
00:26:54,600 --> 00:26:56,350
It should be the smell of disinfectant.

544
00:26:56,350 --> 00:26:57,830
This smell is expected

545
00:26:57,830 --> 00:26:59,290
during routine cleaning.

546
00:27:00,110 --> 00:27:01,110
This way, please.

547
00:27:04,830 --> 00:27:05,790
Mr. Ji,

548
00:27:05,810 --> 00:27:08,000
this is our executive lounge.

549
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:09,590
It is an exclusive space designed

550
00:27:09,590 --> 00:27:11,510
for our VIP guests on the executive floor,

551
00:27:11,510 --> 00:27:14,000
providing exquisite dining

552
00:27:14,000 --> 00:27:16,460
and personalized service around the clock.

553
00:27:22,880 --> 00:27:24,200
If you're interested later,

554
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:25,930
you can come and experience it.

555
00:27:58,590 --> 00:27:59,550
So,

556
00:27:59,880 --> 00:28:02,590
Mr. Ji, are you satisfied with the tour?

557
00:28:03,890 --> 00:28:05,090
I'm curious

558
00:28:05,120 --> 00:28:06,000
how Purong Hotel

559
00:28:06,000 --> 00:28:07,310
keeps its guests now.

560
00:28:08,550 --> 00:28:09,510
I'm sorry?

561
00:28:11,200 --> 00:28:13,110
Your front desk staff is slack,

562
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:15,240
and the hallways smell like disinfectant.

563
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:16,640
After this tour you gave me,

564
00:28:16,640 --> 00:28:18,170
do you think I'm satisfied?

565
00:28:22,280 --> 00:28:23,200
Mr. Ji.

566
00:28:23,230 --> 00:28:24,030
I...

567
00:28:24,050 --> 00:28:25,380
That's not what I meant.

568
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:27,960
Mr. Ji,

569
00:28:28,310 --> 00:28:30,740
you're our distinguished Black Card VIP.

570
00:28:30,790 --> 00:28:32,030
I'm your butler, Yin Xiang.

571
00:28:32,030 --> 00:28:33,830
Feel free to contact me
if you need anything.

572
00:28:33,830 --> 00:28:35,830
-Okay. Thank you.
-Enjoy your stay.

573
00:28:39,350 --> 00:28:39,720
Well.

574
00:28:39,720 --> 00:28:40,550
Let's go.

575
00:28:40,550 --> 00:28:41,880
Is he crazy?

576
00:28:43,640 --> 00:28:45,310
We have a difficult Black Card VIP.

577
00:28:45,310 --> 00:28:46,270
His surname is Ji.

578
00:28:46,270 --> 00:28:47,530
Everyone, be careful.

579
00:29:19,200 --> 00:29:21,720
This is your future service standard

580
00:29:22,310 --> 00:29:24,640
and the service attitude you must uphold.

581
00:29:25,880 --> 00:29:28,480
Today is your first day on the job.

582
00:29:28,550 --> 00:29:31,480
I want you to listen carefully

583
00:29:31,480 --> 00:29:33,310
to what I have to say next.

584
00:29:33,830 --> 00:29:35,830
In the future, no matter

585
00:29:35,830 --> 00:29:38,350
which position you rotate to in the hotel,

586
00:29:38,350 --> 00:29:39,880
you must firmly remember:

587
00:29:40,030 --> 00:29:41,400
Making guests feel at home

588
00:29:41,400 --> 00:29:44,110
is the service tenet of our Purong Hotel.

589
00:29:44,310 --> 00:29:47,380
It might sound a bit cliché,

590
00:29:47,590 --> 00:29:49,030
but I believe

591
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:51,950
it's the foundation of our hotel service.

592
00:29:52,110 --> 00:29:54,160
When a guest walks into the hotel,

593
00:29:54,270 --> 00:29:56,670
every part of our hotel

594
00:29:56,690 --> 00:29:58,780
starts working for them.

595
00:29:58,810 --> 00:30:01,000
We need to keenly perceive

596
00:30:01,020 --> 00:30:03,020
every need of the guest

597
00:30:03,050 --> 00:30:05,900
and cater to all their senses,

598
00:30:06,350 --> 00:30:10,160
providing service
more caring than being at home.

599
00:30:10,180 --> 00:30:12,260
Purong Hotel was established

600
00:30:12,350 --> 00:30:13,810
nearly half a century ago,

601
00:30:13,880 --> 00:30:16,640
and this is how we retain our guests.

602
00:30:17,460 --> 00:30:19,400
In your future work,

603
00:30:19,430 --> 00:30:20,630
I hope

604
00:30:20,680 --> 00:30:23,110
in every service,

605
00:30:23,130 --> 00:30:24,370
you can understand

606
00:30:24,400 --> 00:30:26,800
the meaning of working in a hotel.

607
00:30:26,820 --> 00:30:28,340
This is also the value

608
00:30:28,370 --> 00:30:30,170
that Purong provides you.

609
00:31:28,140 --> 00:31:31,490
[Hotel Manager] [Details]

610
00:31:31,590 --> 00:31:32,380
[Requirements: At least 5 years of
experience in hotel management]

611
00:31:32,400 --> 00:31:33,490
[and operations. Base salary:
8,000 RMB + commission]

612
00:31:39,430 --> 00:31:40,600
[Compensation & Benefitst]

613
00:31:40,600 --> 00:31:42,520
[Salary Expectation (Monthly, RMB)]

614
00:31:44,160 --> 00:31:45,510
[Salary Expectation (Monthly, RMB)]

615
00:31:45,540 --> 00:31:47,680
[Compensation & Benefitst]

616
00:31:55,110 --> 00:31:55,750
Come.

617
00:31:55,770 --> 00:31:57,780
Here. Be careful.

618
00:32:02,230 --> 00:32:02,920
Okay.

619
00:32:03,890 --> 00:32:04,820
Come.

620
00:32:06,730 --> 00:32:08,530
The room might not be big,

621
00:32:08,560 --> 00:32:09,920
but the location is great.

622
00:32:09,920 --> 00:32:11,500
Transport is convenient.

623
00:32:11,530 --> 00:32:13,640
You step right out into the downtown area.

624
00:32:13,640 --> 00:32:16,400
And look, your bed is up here.

625
00:32:16,510 --> 00:32:17,830
It's very private.

626
00:32:17,830 --> 00:32:19,110
4,000 yuan a month.

627
00:32:19,110 --> 00:32:20,370
It's really a bargain.

628
00:32:22,130 --> 00:32:24,600
Can you make it a bit cheaper?

629
00:32:28,380 --> 00:32:29,290
How about this?

630
00:32:29,640 --> 00:32:31,590
If you can

631
00:32:31,650 --> 00:32:33,570
pay 6 months' rent at once,

632
00:32:33,880 --> 00:32:36,000
I'll let you have it for 3,500 a month.

633
00:32:36,030 --> 00:32:37,710
That saves you 3,000 in total.

634
00:32:37,730 --> 00:32:38,430
Okay.

635
00:32:38,450 --> 00:32:39,340
Deal.

636
00:32:39,370 --> 00:32:39,910
Great.

637
00:32:41,080 --> 00:32:42,160
Here, scan my code.

638
00:32:43,260 --> 00:32:43,480
[Loading]

639
00:32:46,150 --> 00:32:47,740
[Payment to Individual: RMB 21,000]

640
00:32:50,350 --> 00:32:51,240
All right.

641
00:32:51,680 --> 00:32:53,200
Keep this key.

642
00:32:53,750 --> 00:32:54,480
And you can

643
00:32:54,480 --> 00:32:55,400
tidy up by yourself.

644
00:32:55,400 --> 00:32:56,640
I'll get going now.

645
00:32:57,110 --> 00:32:57,480
Alright.

646
00:32:57,480 --> 00:32:58,350
Thank you.

647
00:32:58,350 --> 00:32:59,070
Bye.

648
00:33:03,430 --> 00:33:04,610
[My balance: 1,407 yuan]

649
00:33:12,360 --> 00:33:13,550
Hello.

650
00:33:16,440 --> 00:33:17,030
Yes, it's me.

651
00:33:17,030 --> 00:33:18,360
I submitted the resume.

652
00:33:19,590 --> 00:33:20,590
Okay.

653
00:33:20,590 --> 00:33:21,790
I'll be right there.

654
00:33:24,410 --> 00:33:30,640
[Xiaoma Hotel]

655
00:33:26,890 --> 00:33:27,440
I remember

656
00:33:27,440 --> 00:33:28,310
your resume.

657
00:33:29,310 --> 00:33:31,100
After being a housewife for 10 years,

658
00:33:31,100 --> 00:33:33,660
do you think you are up to this job?

659
00:33:33,690 --> 00:33:35,020
Well, ma'am,

660
00:33:35,090 --> 00:33:37,440
although I don't have
much work experience,

661
00:33:37,440 --> 00:33:38,830
I graduated from Hushi University

662
00:33:38,830 --> 00:33:40,690
with a major in hotel management.

663
00:33:40,720 --> 00:33:43,030
When it comes to
handling practical matters,

664
00:33:43,030 --> 00:33:44,420
I also have some experience.

665
00:33:44,420 --> 00:33:46,680
For instance, I handle
our family's utility bills

666
00:33:46,680 --> 00:33:48,830
and commercial insurance contracts...

667
00:33:48,830 --> 00:33:50,270
We are a hotel.

668
00:33:50,300 --> 00:33:52,740
Do you understand
the current hotel business?

669
00:33:52,740 --> 00:33:53,740
My husband...

670
00:33:56,370 --> 00:33:58,770
I've stayed in many hotels
in recent years.

671
00:33:59,080 --> 00:34:01,120
And regarding hotel management knowledge,

672
00:34:01,120 --> 00:34:02,130
I haven't let it slip either.

673
00:34:02,130 --> 00:34:03,180
What kind of hotels have you stayed in?

674
00:34:03,180 --> 00:34:04,130
Many.

675
00:34:04,160 --> 00:34:06,000
Like Aman in Japan

676
00:34:06,020 --> 00:34:08,139
and Banyan Tree in Morocco.

677
00:34:08,440 --> 00:34:09,770
Also...

678
00:34:09,860 --> 00:34:11,139
[Xiaoma Hotel]

679
00:34:13,030 --> 00:34:14,400
Hampton by Hilton

680
00:34:14,429 --> 00:34:15,960
and Fairfield by Marriott.

681
00:34:16,030 --> 00:34:16,920
Even budget hotels

682
00:34:16,920 --> 00:34:18,070
like Home Inn and Hanting,

683
00:34:18,070 --> 00:34:19,400
I've stayed in them too.

684
00:34:22,409 --> 00:34:23,679
I know your concerns.

685
00:34:24,190 --> 00:34:25,590
In terms of work experience,

686
00:34:25,590 --> 00:34:27,070
I am indeed lacking.

687
00:34:27,090 --> 00:34:29,290
So I am willing to start from the basics

688
00:34:29,310 --> 00:34:30,580
and I will work hard to catch up.

689
00:34:30,580 --> 00:34:31,850
Here,

690
00:34:32,150 --> 00:34:33,440
we actually value

691
00:34:33,440 --> 00:34:35,040
practical business skills.

692
00:34:35,120 --> 00:34:36,400
If we let you start right away,

693
00:34:36,400 --> 00:34:37,400
can you handle it?

694
00:34:37,560 --> 00:34:38,389
I can.

695
00:34:38,449 --> 00:34:39,590
[Xiaoma Hotel]

696
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:40,949
Welcome to the team.

697
00:34:44,230 --> 00:34:45,880
Am I hired just like that?

698
00:34:46,030 --> 00:34:47,739
What about the salary and benefits?

699
00:34:47,739 --> 00:34:48,889
The position you interviewed for

700
00:34:48,889 --> 00:34:50,070
has already been filled.

701
00:34:50,070 --> 00:34:50,760
However,

702
00:34:50,780 --> 00:34:52,960
we can transfer you to a sales position.

703
00:34:52,960 --> 00:34:54,929
This position is commission-based.

704
00:34:54,929 --> 00:34:57,610
The base salary is 3,500 yuan a month.

705
00:34:57,860 --> 00:34:59,320
Is that acceptable to you?

706
00:35:00,020 --> 00:35:00,860
I see.

707
00:35:01,070 --> 00:35:02,070
Ms. Xu,

708
00:35:02,070 --> 00:35:03,960
your competitive advantage is not obvious,

709
00:35:03,960 --> 00:35:06,400
and you have a 10-year
gap in your work experience.

710
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:07,690
Given your current qualifications,

711
00:35:07,690 --> 00:35:10,420
this is the best offer we can make.

712
00:35:09,350 --> 00:35:11,760
[Xiaoma Hotel Labor Contract]

713
00:35:21,560 --> 00:35:23,800
Can I get a 2-month advance on my salary?

714
00:35:23,820 --> 00:35:26,260
You can't get an advance during probation.

715
00:35:26,910 --> 00:35:28,660
I'm really in a tight spot.

716
00:35:28,790 --> 00:35:29,790
Tell you what,

717
00:35:29,810 --> 00:35:31,510
we happen to have a client today.

718
00:35:31,510 --> 00:35:32,760
If you go and win him over,

719
00:35:32,760 --> 00:35:34,510
the bonus is 5,000.

720
00:35:34,550 --> 00:35:35,680
How do I win him over?

721
00:35:36,090 --> 00:35:37,260
Ms. Xu,

722
00:35:37,670 --> 00:35:40,130
you have to figure out
how to work on your own.

723
00:35:42,300 --> 00:35:44,900
Then please send me
the client's information.

724
00:35:44,940 --> 00:35:45,750
Okay.

725
00:35:58,030 --> 00:35:58,880
Hello?

726
00:35:58,900 --> 00:36:00,700
Mr. Mai, I've arrived.

727
00:36:02,810 --> 00:36:04,130
Where are you?

728
00:36:05,670 --> 00:36:06,800
I... I can't hear you.

729
00:36:06,800 --> 00:36:07,510
What did you say?

730
00:36:07,510 --> 00:36:08,840
Hello?

731
00:36:13,300 --> 00:36:14,430
You wanted to see me?

732
00:36:14,730 --> 00:36:15,520
Qiaoqi.

733
00:36:15,540 --> 00:36:16,590
We've only been dating for a month.

734
00:36:16,590 --> 00:36:18,070
You can't just break up with me like that.

735
00:36:18,070 --> 00:36:20,000
If I did something wrong,

736
00:36:20,020 --> 00:36:21,610
-Tell me. I can...
-Stop. Stop.

737
00:36:21,610 --> 00:36:22,880
I'll make it short.

738
00:36:23,010 --> 00:36:24,590
I don't do long-term relationships.

739
00:36:24,590 --> 00:36:26,170
Getting back together
is absolutely impossible.

740
00:36:26,170 --> 00:36:27,150
If you really need
something in the future,

741
00:36:27,150 --> 00:36:28,570
you're always welcome to find me.

742
00:36:28,570 --> 00:36:30,260
But if you try to harass me,

743
00:36:30,290 --> 00:36:31,820
I'll pull all your hair out.

744
00:36:36,580 --> 00:36:38,520
Hello? What?

745
00:36:38,550 --> 00:36:40,070
Over here.

746
00:36:40,490 --> 00:36:41,480
Mr. Mai.

747
00:36:41,500 --> 00:36:43,400
-I'm with Xiaoma Hotel...
-I've been waiting for you.

748
00:36:43,400 --> 00:36:45,230
Have a seat.

749
00:36:45,500 --> 00:36:46,600
Ms. Xu.

750
00:36:47,210 --> 00:36:49,760
Actually, you can make money

751
00:36:49,840 --> 00:36:51,760
off me so easily.

752
00:36:52,640 --> 00:36:55,050
Finish this drink, and I'll sign.

753
00:36:55,210 --> 00:36:57,170
Finish it.

754
00:36:57,190 --> 00:36:58,730
Finish it.

755
00:36:59,400 --> 00:37:00,230
Finish it.

756
00:37:01,250 --> 00:37:02,040
Okay.

757
00:37:03,760 --> 00:37:06,140
Great!

758
00:37:06,170 --> 00:37:08,180
Good drinker.

759
00:37:08,410 --> 00:37:09,330
Impressive.

760
00:37:09,360 --> 00:37:11,920
You can really hold your liquor, Ms. Xu.

761
00:37:11,920 --> 00:37:13,230
Great.

762
00:37:13,430 --> 00:37:14,690
Ms. Xu, please...

763
00:37:16,540 --> 00:37:18,540
We all came out to have fun.

764
00:37:18,560 --> 00:37:20,210
No need to be so shy.

765
00:37:20,240 --> 00:37:22,210
I'm actually very gentle.

766
00:37:24,740 --> 00:37:25,770
You're unbelievable!

767
00:37:25,770 --> 00:37:27,080
How dare you push me!

768
00:37:27,560 --> 00:37:29,680
Didn't your mother
ever tell you not to hit women?

769
00:37:29,680 --> 00:37:30,760
What are you standing around for?

770
00:37:30,760 --> 00:37:31,510
Get them!

771
00:37:32,880 --> 00:37:33,710
Let's go.

772
00:37:34,010 --> 00:37:35,470
Darn it!

773
00:37:45,310 --> 00:37:46,880
What's going on with you, Xu Miyu?

774
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:47,770
Instead of staying at home,

775
00:37:47,770 --> 00:37:48,900
you came here to drink with clients?

776
00:37:48,900 --> 00:37:50,360
Do you think this is a game?

777
00:37:51,880 --> 00:37:52,920
I got divorced.

778
00:37:53,180 --> 00:37:54,140
What did you say?

779
00:37:56,320 --> 00:37:57,150
Wait.

780
00:37:57,170 --> 00:37:58,360
What exactly happened?

781
00:37:58,360 --> 00:37:59,240
I got divorced.

782
00:38:00,960 --> 00:38:02,360
I have nothing left.

783
00:38:21,410 --> 00:38:22,330
Then...

784
00:38:22,890 --> 00:38:24,220
About your divorce,

785
00:38:24,250 --> 00:38:25,560
do your parents know?

786
00:38:26,570 --> 00:38:28,090
I wouldn't dare tell them.

787
00:38:28,600 --> 00:38:29,880
In their eyes,

788
00:38:29,880 --> 00:38:31,810
I finally found a good man to marry,

789
00:38:31,870 --> 00:38:33,730
so they can stop worrying about me

790
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:35,370
and enjoy a good life.

791
00:38:35,390 --> 00:38:37,900
If I tell them I'm divorced now

792
00:38:38,070 --> 00:38:39,730
and still haven't found a job,

793
00:38:40,340 --> 00:38:42,870
how can they hold
their heads high in the town?

794
00:38:44,290 --> 00:38:45,520
Xu Miyu.

795
00:38:45,550 --> 00:38:46,760
You know what I've hated most about you

796
00:38:46,760 --> 00:38:48,190
since we were kids?

797
00:38:48,340 --> 00:38:50,330
You only care about what others think

798
00:38:50,330 --> 00:38:52,130
and never think about yourself.

799
00:38:53,290 --> 00:38:54,790
You finally have your freedom now.

800
00:38:54,790 --> 00:38:57,050
Can you please care more about yourself?

801
00:39:03,280 --> 00:39:04,080
You're right.

802
00:39:04,650 --> 00:39:05,670
That's what I was thinking too.

803
00:39:05,670 --> 00:39:06,710
So lately,

804
00:39:06,740 --> 00:39:09,450
I've been trying hard to find a hotel job.

805
00:39:10,090 --> 00:39:11,190
I want to

806
00:39:11,730 --> 00:39:12,800
go back to 10 years ago,

807
00:39:12,800 --> 00:39:14,550
to the turning point that changed my life,

808
00:39:14,550 --> 00:39:16,480
and see if, through my own efforts,

809
00:39:16,710 --> 00:39:18,480
I can realize my own value.

810
00:39:18,480 --> 00:39:20,000
That's the spirit.

811
00:39:20,970 --> 00:39:22,880
But if you want a hotel job,

812
00:39:22,880 --> 00:39:24,360
why didn't you tell me?

813
00:39:24,360 --> 00:39:25,480
Didn't I tell you last time

814
00:39:25,480 --> 00:39:27,010
that I work at Purong Hotel?

815
00:39:27,230 --> 00:39:29,400
Why would Purong Hotel hire me?

816
00:39:29,420 --> 00:39:30,660
I'm not qualified.

817
00:39:30,690 --> 00:39:33,120
A famous 5-star hotel in Shanghai.

818
00:39:33,150 --> 00:39:34,970
I can't even reach it on my tiptoes.

819
00:39:34,970 --> 00:39:35,760
If you can't reach it,

820
00:39:35,760 --> 00:39:37,460
why don't you get a ladder?

821
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:38,920
I am your ladder.

822
00:39:41,110 --> 00:39:42,150
It's just that

823
00:39:42,260 --> 00:39:44,720
your ex-husband
is in the tourism industry.

824
00:39:44,760 --> 00:39:46,840
He'll inevitably deal with Purong.

825
00:39:47,070 --> 00:39:49,310
If you really join Purong,

826
00:39:49,760 --> 00:39:50,440
and in case

827
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:52,400
you guys run into each other,

828
00:39:52,800 --> 00:39:54,110
you need to be mentally prepared.

829
00:39:54,110 --> 00:39:55,050
I don't care.

830
00:39:55,630 --> 00:39:57,960
I just want to do
what I want to do right now.

831
00:39:59,200 --> 00:40:01,110
I'm relieved to hear that.

832
00:40:04,070 --> 00:40:05,510
Our hotel's marketing department

833
00:40:05,510 --> 00:40:06,900
has an interview tomorrow.

834
00:40:06,900 --> 00:40:08,360
I've referred you.

835
00:40:08,630 --> 00:40:09,960
Someone will add you on WeChat later.

836
00:40:09,960 --> 00:40:11,220
Remember to accept it.

837
00:40:11,480 --> 00:40:13,170
Thank you, Qiaoqi.

838
00:40:13,940 --> 00:40:15,310
I will definitely work hard.

839
00:40:15,310 --> 00:40:16,830
It's just a small favor.

840
00:40:16,850 --> 00:40:18,580
I can't just shove you in there.

841
00:40:18,580 --> 00:40:19,880
I already feel like

842
00:40:19,880 --> 00:40:21,830
I'm getting something for nothing.

843
00:40:21,830 --> 00:40:23,910
You didn't get something for nothing.

844
00:40:23,910 --> 00:40:25,850
You just lost too much.

845
00:40:27,210 --> 00:40:29,340
Good thing you cut your losses in time.

846
00:40:29,630 --> 00:40:30,360
From now on,

847
00:40:30,840 --> 00:40:32,100
it'll all be good days.

848
00:40:34,650 --> 00:40:36,580
From now on, it'll all be good days.

849
00:40:37,060 --> 00:40:37,790
Cheers.

850
00:40:59,350 --> 00:41:00,100
Hello.

851
00:41:00,150 --> 00:41:01,110
Mr. Yang, what's wrong?

852
00:41:01,110 --> 00:41:02,070
Are you off work?

853
00:41:02,070 --> 00:41:02,960
Yes, I am.

854
00:41:03,150 --> 00:41:04,280
But don't worry.

855
00:41:04,380 --> 00:41:05,970
I've already made an appointment
with tomorrow's client.

856
00:41:05,970 --> 00:41:07,550
He'll come to the company in the afternoon
to go over the contract.

857
00:41:07,550 --> 00:41:08,070
Okay, okay.

858
00:41:08,070 --> 00:41:08,960
Stop talking.

859
00:41:09,190 --> 00:41:10,540
Come to the company tomorrow,

860
00:41:10,540 --> 00:41:12,420
hand over the clients you have,

861
00:41:12,440 --> 00:41:14,170
and don't come to work anymore.

862
00:41:14,330 --> 00:41:15,370
What do you mean?

863
00:41:15,400 --> 00:41:16,630
You're asking me?

864
00:41:16,880 --> 00:41:18,590
I've lost all my face because of you.

865
00:41:18,590 --> 00:41:19,800
The video of Mrs. Nie at the banquet

866
00:41:19,800 --> 00:41:21,880
talking about you being a mistress

867
00:41:21,880 --> 00:41:23,710
has already reached the clients.

868
00:41:23,710 --> 00:41:25,700
How dare you stay at the hotel?

869
00:41:25,800 --> 00:41:27,390
Don't you care about Yuhua's reputation?

870
00:41:27,390 --> 00:41:28,500
Come handle your resignation tomorrow.

